@startuml
actor "Sales Agent" as SA
participant "CRM System" as CRM
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Report Generator" as RG

SA -> CRM: Search Customer
CRM -> DB: Query Customer Data
DB --> CRM: Return Customer Info
SA -> CRM: Log New Interaction
CRM -> DB: Save Interaction Record
SA -> CRM: Request Customer Report
CRM -> RG: Generate Report
RG --> CRM: Report Ready
CRM -> SA: Deliver Report
@enduml
